\newlabel{SItab:fisher_pos_sel}{{S8}{}{Fisher's exact test for enrichment of number of positively selected genes on X compared to A split by sex-bias categories. Raw and Benjamini-Hochberg corrected p-values are shown, significance highlighted in bold.\relax }{table.caption.39}{}}
